        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preventing Vigilante Stalking that Stops Women's Access to Healthcare and Abortion Rights Act of 2021</strong> </p> <p>This bill increases the maximum prison term for a stalking offense, if the offense is committed with the intent to obtain health care information of an individual or to prevent the health care decisions of an individual.</p>]]>
        </text>
